        "content": "True passive (less common in Spanish):\n                  → Las cartas fueron enviadas ayer. = The letters were sent yesterday.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "spanish": "El libro fue escrito por Cervantes.",
            "english": "The book was written by Cervantes."
