            "spanish": "La casa será vendida mañana.",
            "english": "The house will be sold tomorrow."
          },
          {
            "spanish": "Las cartas fueron enviadas ayer.",
            "english": "The letters were sent yesterday."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "lesson",
        "heading": "Se Pasiva (More Common)",
        "content": "SE + verb (3rd person) - agent unknown:\n                        → ¿Cómo se dice 'hello'? = How do you say 'hello'?",
        "examples": [
          {
            "spanish": "Se habla español aquí.",
            "english": "Spanish is spoken here."
          },
          {
            "spanish": "Se venden casas.",
            "english": "Houses are sold. (Houses for sale)"
