          },
          {
            "spanish": "¿Cómo se dice 'hello'?",
            "english": "How do you say 'hello'?"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "lesson",
        "heading": "Se Impersonal",
        "content": "SE + verb (3rd singular) for 'one/you/people':\n                  \n   ✏️ Exercise: ¿Cómo ___ 'goodbye' en español?",
        "examples": [
          {
            "spanish": "Se come bien aquí.",
            "english": "One eats well here."
          },
          {
