            "english": "They say it's going to rain."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "lesson",
        "heading": "Relative Pronouns",
        "content": "Connecting clauses:\n                              → cuyo/cuya = whose",
        "examples": [
          {
            "spanish": "que",
            "english": "that/which/who (most common)"
