          {
            "spanish": "quien/quienes",
            "english": "who (for people, after preposition)"
          },
          {
            "spanish": "el que/la que/los que/las que",
            "english": "the one who/which"
          },
          {
            "spanish": "lo que",
            "english": "what/that which (abstract)"
          },
          {
            "spanish": "cuyo/cuya",
            "english": "whose"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "lesson",
        "heading": "Relative Pronoun Examples",
        "content": "In context:\n                        \n   ✏️ Exercise: ___ me dijiste es interesante.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "spanish": "El hombre que vi era alto.",
            "english": "The man (that) I saw was tall."
          },
          {
            "spanish": "La mujer con quien hablé...",
            "english": "The woman with whom I spoke..."
          },
          {
            "spanish": "Lo que dices es verdad.",
            "english": "What you say is true."
          },
          {
            "spanish": "La ciudad donde nací...",
            "english": "The city where I was born..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "lesson",
        "heading": "POR - Uses",
        "content": "Through, because of, exchange, duration, per:\n                              → Per: Tres veces por semana. = Three times per week.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "spanish": "Cause: Por la lluvia, no salí.",
            "english": "Because of the rain, I didn't go out."
          },
          {
            "spanish": "Exchange: Pagué $10 por el libro.",
            "english": "I paid $10 for the book."
          },
          {
            "spanish": "Duration: Estudié por tres horas.",
            "english": "I studied for three hours."
          },
          {
            "spanish": "Through: Caminé por el parque.",
            "english": "I walked through the park."
          },
          {
            "spanish": "Per: Tres veces por semana.",
            "english": "Three times per week."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "lesson",
        "heading": "PARA - Uses",
        "content": "Purpose, destination, deadline, recipient, opinion:\n                              \n   ✏️ Exercise: Este libro es ___ mi madre. (recipient)\n\n   ✏️ Exercise: Gracias ___ ayudarme. (cause/reason)",
